          <p>Framework enforces security, performance, and scalability patterns.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit">
          <h3>üìö Better Documentation</h3>
          <p>Focused examples and guides for real-world scenarios.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit">
          <h3>üîó Framework Features</h3>
          <p>Middleware, request context, response utilities built-in.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Next Steps -->
  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Next Steps</h2>

      <div class="next-steps">
        <div class="step">
          <h3><a href="/cloudflare-workers-guide">üìñ Deep Dive: Cloudflare Workers Guide</a></h3>
